### Variables
@host = http://localhost:5053
@tenantId = 3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# AVERAGE TICKET
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Ticket promedio — último mes
GET {{host}}/insights/average-ticket?from=2025-01-01&to=2025-01-31
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Ticket promedio — último trimestre
GET {{host}}/insights/average-ticket?from=2024-10-01&to=2024-12-31
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# CANCELLATION RATE
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Tasa de cancelación — último mes
GET {{host}}/insights/cancellation-rate?from=2025-01-01&to=2025-01-31
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Tasa de cancelación — últimos 3 meses
GET {{host}}/insights/cancellation-rate?from=2024-10-01&to=2024-12-31
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# DAILY SUMMARY
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Resumen diario — última semana
GET {{host}}/insights/daily-summary?from=2025-01-20&to=2025-01-26
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Resumen diario — último mes (máx. 90 días)
GET {{host}}/insights/daily-summary?from=2025-01-01&to=2025-01-31
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# CASOS DE ERROR
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Error: from > to
GET {{host}}/insights/average-ticket?from=2025-02-01&to=2025-01-01
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###

### Error: rango > 90 días en daily-summary
GET {{host}}/insights/daily-summary?from=2024-01-01&to=2024-06-01
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

###
